0ccb1477-b933-4d0c-a43f-cd89e6d018f4:
The doctors are ultimate and very down to earth human being .
I m 100 % satisfied with the treatment and other facilities.
But admission department specially CGHS department head Mr Sandeep Dawar needs to learn how to talk with decency and respect with CGHS beneficiaries and their attendant .
He is most arrogant person I have ever meet in my life . He always talk rudely and never wants to explain the process . He always wants to escape from any meeting or conversation.
It is pathetic and hurtful to see this kind of human behaviour in this top class hospital.
Higher authority must look after these issues and give clear instructions to communicate with everyone humbly and respectfully.

Because everyone is entitled to treat with decency and dignity. These kind of human behaviour is distorting the image of the hospital.

Rest hospital management is mature enough to understand the situation.

My best wishes to Medanta hospital and special thanks to Dr Naresh ji , Dr Sanjay Mittal ji & team and All who helped me.

Thank you üôè
